These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, architect
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, skiing
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, ship
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | cooking       | baking |
| Job         | architect | librarian  |
| Sport       | skiing    | climbing    |
| Transport   | ship       | roller      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, drama
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the dancer is on the far left##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | milk     | mirinda |
| Job           | dancer | journalist      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | documentary      |
| Sport         | volleyball | basketball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea
There 2 different types of food: kale, watermelon
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, trike
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person eating kale is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | tea  |
| Food          | kale    | watermelon   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | hip-hop   |
| Transport     | trike     | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
