.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, cranberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, hip-hop
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
2 different pets are kept: fish, bird
1. the thai is the owner of the bird##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the thai is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | pepper | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | hip-hop      |
| Nationality   | italian | thai    |
| Pet           | fish    | bird    |

